data.description: This is it! The Wait is over! This 4 bedroom 4 bath home is located in a private setting and sitting on 5 acres. All mechanicals are newer. Home has two wood burning fire places including one in the master bedroom. All kitchen appliances included. Beautiful heated pool with a two tier deck is ready to entertain friends and family this season. Upon entry take note of the vaulted ceilings and open loft to upstairs. The living and dining areas are spacious and the separate family room with fireplace is ideal for move nights or just falling asleep by the fire. There is also a basement that offers endless potential along with a bathroom. The natural wooded privacy is a rare find! Schedule your tour today.
